  "1619580": {
    "name": "Slopecrashers",
    "steam_appid": 1619580,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619580/extras/5a7ccfca9b26170ff149b88306899d58.poster.avif?t=1754641152\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619580/extras/5a7ccfca9b26170ff149b88306899d58.webm?t=1754641152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619580/extras/5a7ccfca9b26170ff149b88306899d58.mp4?t=1754641152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>所有自由滑雪者、粉雪爱好者和派对游戏迷看过来！无论你追求的是复古的滑雪情怀，还是和朋友的激烈竞速，《Slopecrashers》都能满足你！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619580/extras/535c346bcd9d71590c41c46cd6f72b89.poster.avif?t=1754641152\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619580/extras/535c346bcd9d71590c41c46cd6f72b89.webm?t=1754641152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619580/extras/535c346bcd9d71590c41c46cd6f72b89.mp4?t=1754641152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跃入轻松上手、挑战极限的滑雪混战世界，与你的可自定义动物队伍一起狂欢！《Slopecrashers》灵感源自街机竞速经典，由次世代物理引擎驱动，将竞速、特技和连招推向巅峰。不止是滑雪板——拿起平底锅，也能在雪地、沙滩或赛博城市中横扫20条赛道！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619580/extras/13210134e27fe5096b52dd01db1527c4.poster.avif?t=1754641152\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619580/extras/13210134e27fe5096b52dd01db1527c4.webm?t=1754641152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619580/extras/13210134e27fe5096b52dd01db1527c4.mp4?t=1754641152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>为啥你会爱上 Slopecrashers</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🏂 轻松上手，技巧无限</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持最多8人游戏，炫技特技、连击组合、狂飙加速，应有尽有！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🎉 派对或线上都精彩</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本地四人分屏或线上对战都超欢乐，奶奶都能加入（需联网，嘴炮随意）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🛠 疯狂道具、爆笑玩法</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喷气背包、钩爪、火箭推进器一应俱全，还能释放爆炸、鼹鼠等混乱技能。想悠闲？试试无道具或无对手模式！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🌎 赛道不限雪地</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雪山、热带岛屿、未来都市等20条独特赛道，永不停歇的刺激体验等你来！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619580/extras/c445c42315afd0cf704cd62126301de0.poster.avif?t=1754641152\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619580/extras/c445c42315afd0cf704cd62126301de0.webm?t=1754641152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619580/extras/c445c42315afd0cf704cd62126301de0.mp4?t=1754641152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>带来欢乐的功能亮点</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 个有配音的疯狂卡通动物角色</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位角色约 90 种自定义选项</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >38 个疯狂“滑雪板”（锅也算！）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25 个改变玩法的工具，如喷气包、钩爪等</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种模式：竞速、绕杆、特技秀与 Boss 战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奖励丰厚的特技与连招系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本地最多 4 人/在线最多 8 人比赛</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619580/extras/cfda2f77c7c121d8db929811b19dcfda.poster.avif?t=1754641152\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619580/extras/cfda2f77c7c121d8db929811b19dcfda.webm?t=1754641152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619580/extras/cfda2f77c7c121d8db929811b19dcfda.mp4?t=1754641152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >适合各种心情的模式</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战役模式：挑战全球 126 个手工设计的赛事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大奖赛模式：赢得 7 个奖杯，填满你的奖杯柜。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >街机模式：打造属于你的无限定制锦标赛。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分屏模式：任何模式都可与好友本地游玩。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619580/extras/e6b05c097cc2830929cf41af808ec830.poster.avif?t=1754641152\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619580/extras/e6b05c097cc2830929cf41af808ec830.webm?t=1754641152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619580/extras/e6b05c097cc2830929cf41af808ec830.mp4?t=1754641152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >我们不需要雪也能滑行！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好比赛、疯狂特技和释放纯粹混乱的时刻吧！无论你是竞速达人、聚会游戏爱好者，还是只是想看企鹅做1080旋转，Slopecrashers 都会让你欲罢不能！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >街机风格的滑雪竞速来了。准备好成为终极 Slopecrasher 吗？</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 韩语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 简体中文, 繁体中文, 荷兰语, 瑞典语",
